📦 Inventory Management System
A user-friendly, feature-rich desktop application built using Python, Tkinter, and Object-Oriented Programming principles to help manage product inventories efficiently.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Language: Python

GUI: Tkinter

Data Storage: File Handling (Text/CSV)

Visualization: Matplotlib

🎯 Key Features
🔍 Search & Filter items by Category or Quantity

⚠️ Low Stock Alerts for items below threshold

📤 Export Inventory Data to CSV file

🌗 Light/Dark Mode Toggle for better UX

↩️ Undo/Redo Functionality for accidental actions

📊 Graphical Reports (bar/line charts for stock overview)

✏️ Update Quantity or Price using Item ID or Name

✅ Add, View, Delete inventory items easily

🧠 Clean & intuitive GUI for non-technical users


How to Run
                     
Make sure Python is installed (>= 3.8)

Install required modules (if any):

bash
Copy code
pip install matplotlib
Run the app:

bash
Copy code
python main.py



